Developer Terms of Use
des:
Get the latest information from WALB News 10 Albany, Georgia within Alexa's Flash Briefing.

Enable this Skill, then say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing" or "Alexa, what's in the news" to hear the audio.

Feeds include the latest weather forecast for the Albany, Georgia area from the WALB News 10 Weather team.
